Well today was pretty good I got a really sweet card from one of my best friends Josh and some candy it was really good but I also got to tell my friends how great my Valentines day was so maybe they will finally start thinking Chris is not that bad of a guy but I think hes great no matter what they say so I guess it Doesn't really matter anyway 
 About My Valentines Day 
 I finally got up on time and straighten my hair so I was looking pretty cute if you ask me lol well I got to school and gave all my friends there home made cards and gave Chris his I really hope he liked it well so school went along as normal got home and Josh help me pick out what to wear lol he really is a good friend then chris came and got me then we went out to dinner and to his moms work to say Hi then to pizza and brewery to hang with his brother and his friend for a little while then back to his house and hung out for about an hour then I went home I had a really good time he was very sweet I hope he had as good a time as me 
  well I really should get back to my homework before I fail Parenting 

                         LOVE Always
                                  Tabby
